data.description: Welcome to 423 Jasmine Lane situated in the desirable neighborhood of Aragona Village! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home features a large bonus/flex room with endless use options such as another bedroom, playroom, family room, home gym etc..  New LVP & a fresh coat of paint in the main living areas.  The back yard has lots of wooded privacy and is on over an acre of land.  As an added bonus there is a pier with a day dock & access to the community boat ramp providing outside activities within walking distance! You don't want to miss this one! Seller is offering $3,000 use as you choose to the buyer.
